  Cores 2-3:    GM1+Bots1 / Sandbox1  → slot 1
  Cores 4-5:    GM2+Bots2 / Sandbox2  → slot 2
  ...
  Cores 40-41:  GM20+Bots20 / Sandbox20 → slot 20
